high_descs: Turn around and turn right to find the stove.
Open the cabinet on the top right and take out the sponge.
Take the sponge and turn right to find the bowl on the counter.
Place the sponge in the bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Take a few steps left, with the bowl and look up.
Open the top cabinet and place the bowl and sponge inside.
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl and sponge to a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a right at the end of the counter and walk to the black stove ahead.
Open the cabinet above to the right of the stove, pick up the green sponge and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the counter on the left just before the microwave.
Put the sponge into a clear container with a knife on the counter.
Pick up the container with the sponge and the knife inside of it from the counter.
Turn left, walk to the stove and turn right to face the cabinet above to the right of the stove.
Put the container with the sponge and the knife inside the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a container with a knife and a sponge in a cabinet.

take out the sponge in the drawer
turn right and head to the table
drop the sponge on glass bowl on the table
pick up the glass bowl from the table
head up to the drawer
place the glass bowl in the drawer
anns.task_desc: place a sponge in a glass bowl on an overhead drawer
